flowchart TD
  Raw[Raw User Signals<br/>movement, routines, preferences, offer outcomes] --> LocalGraph[Device-Local Knowledge Graph]
  LocalGraph --> Gemma[Local Gemma Runtime]
  Gemma --> Intent[Abstract Intent]

  Context[Non-Personal Context<br/>city, weather, place category, opening status, events] --> Intent
  Intent --> Hermes[Hermes Gateway]
  Hermes --> Gemini[Gemini Public Discovery]
  Gemini --> Insight[Public Deal Intelligence]

  Intent --> OfferEngine[Offer Generation]
  Insight --> OfferEngine
  MerchantRules[Merchant Rules<br/>caps, products, goals, guardrails] --> OfferEngine
  OfferEngine --> Offer[Generated Offer]

  Offer --> QR[QR Token]
  QR --> Validate[Backend Validation]
  Validate --> Ledger[Wallet Ledger]
  Validate --> MerchantAnalytics[Aggregate Merchant Analytics]

  LocalGraph -. not sent .-> Gemini
  Raw -. not sent .-> Hermes
  Raw -. not sent .-> MerchantAnalytics
